She's talented, lively.

202
00:15:33,131 --> 00:15:36,396
l enjoy having her in my class.

203
00:15:36,468 --> 00:15:39,835
Don't forget your pirouette.
Practice!

204
00:15:39,904 --> 00:15:41,838
